data.description: Welcome Home! This beautiful spacious 5 Bedroom and 4 Full bath home with Open Floor Plan and Lots of Natural Light in Popular Ansley Park Community. Large kitchen features Beautiful Granite Countertops, Large Island, Stainless Steel Appliances, White Cabinets and an Open View of the Family Room - Perfect For Entertaining. The Main level also has an Office/formal living room, Dining Room, Bedroom plus a Full Bathroom.       Second floor has Oversized Primary Suite features sitting area, as well as plenty of space for your California king bed. Owners bath offers Double Vanity massive walk in closets, shower and  separate Soaking Tub. The other bedrooms share a jack n jill bathroom and the Fourth bedroom has its own full bathroom. Amazing Backyard Perfect outdoor space for entertaining. Enjoy the community clubhouse, tennis courts, pool and the convenience of Poole's Mill Elementary within walking distance. No short-term Rentals, But HOA allows 1 year or longer leases in subdivision!
